  "instructions": [
    "Heat 1 tablespoon of oil in a large skillet over low heat.",
    "Add the sliced onions and cook, stirring occasionally, for 20 minutes or until caramelized.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for 1 minute, stirring constantly.",
    "Add the eggplant, salt, and red pepper flakes. Cook for 5 minutes, stirring occasionally.",
    "Add the tomatoes and cook for 10 minutes, stirring occasionally.",
    "Transfer the mixture to a serving dish and garnish with parsley.",
    "Serve warm or at room temperature."
